                  , that he wanted a piece of 8d. brown sattin ribbon; and one piece of 8d. brown scarlet sarsnet ribbon, for Joseph Gillman, Richard Wood, and 
                     <persName id="t18170115-81-person632">
                        John 
                        Copling
                     <interp inst="t18170115-81-person632" type="surname" value="Copling"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18170115-81-person632" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18170115-81-person632" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  , by means of which false pretence, he did fraudulently obtain from the said 
                     <persName id="t18170115-81-person633">
                        John 
                        Marshal
                     <interp inst="t18170115-81-person633" type="surname" value="Marshal"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18170115-81-person633" type="given" value="John"></interp>
